query:
SELECT 
  id,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt,
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(createdAt) as created_ts,
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(updatedAt) as updated_ts,
  CAST(createdAt AS CHAR) as created_str,
  CAST(updatedAt AS CHAR) as updated_str
FROM gestantes 
WHERE email = 'teste@gestantesapp.com'
LIMIT 1;
